{"type":"message","id":"ca74b648","parentId":"a18f12b5","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:01:55.248Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-29 09:01:54 GMT+8] Exec completed (oceanic-, code 0) :: 服务给予最高可达30%的补贴，重点向“小巨人”企业和制造业企业倾斜。 * **共享服务平台**：依托国家工业互联网建设共享服务平台。 3. **地方资金支持**：如辽宁安排“智改数转”专项资金。 **四、 支持方向与服务** 1. **十大支持领域**：覆盖传统产业升级、数字基建、数据要素市场培育等多个维度，强调项目创新性与示范效应。 2. **赋能平台建…\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 29th, 2026 — 9:01 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-29 01:01 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774746115245}}
{"type":"message","id":"dc1308ed","parentId":"ca74b648","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:01:59.022Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the HEARTBEAT.md file to understand what needs to be done.","thinkingSignature":"d427a24428a2216572f3b494d35d56298fb29584103cc90d2814d709e01d3f69"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4ry3tx8eb191_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":131,"output":60,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":43010,"totalTokens":43201,"cost":{"input":0.0000393,"output":0.000072,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0051611999999999995,"total":0.005272499999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774746115246}}
{"type":"message","id":"d4fc525e","parentId":"dc1308ed","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:01:59.086Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4ry3tx8eb191_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - 主动任务清单\n\n> 这里是让我能够主动关心姚霖的任务清单\n\n## 每天早上 (8:00-9:00)\n\n1. **检查今日日程**\n   - 查看姚霖今天的日历安排\n   - 主动提醒重要会议或事件\n\n2. **知识库更新**\n   - 检查是否有需要归档的重要信息\n\n## 每天中午 (12:00-13:00)\n\n1. **半日回顾**\n   - 检查上午是否有未处理的重要消息\n\n## 每天晚上 (18:00-20:00)\n\n1. **主动汇报**\n   - 询问姚霖今天是否有需要处理的事情\n\n2. **记忆归档**\n   - 将当天的重要对话整理到 memory/ 文件夹\n\n## 每30分钟执行一次\n\n1. **检查未回复消息** (8:00-22:00)\n   - 获取最近2小时内的私聊消息\n   - 检查是否有他人发送的消息超过5分钟未回复\n   - 分析消息意图，以姚霖身份直接发送AI回复\n   - 回复后通知姚霖已自动回复\n\n## 每周五\n\n1. **周复盘**\n   - 总结本周服务姚霖的情况\n   - 记录做得好和需要改进的地方\n   - 更新 MEMORY.md\n\n## 每周记忆维护\n\n读取 `memory/heartbeat-state.json`，检查 `lastMemoryMaintenance` 字段。如果距今 >= 7天：\n\n1. 读最近7天的 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` 日志\n2. 提炼有价值的信息到 `memory/projects.md` 或 `memory/lessons.md`\n3. 压缩已完成一次性任务的日志为一行结论\n4. 删除过期信息\n5. 更新 `heartbeat-state.json` 的 `lastMemoryMaintenance` 为今天\n\n---\n\n## 触发条件\n\n这些任务会在 heartbeat 触发时自动执行。\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- 指令要明确（路径、动作清晰）\n- 优先处理紧急、重要的事项\n- 不要过度打扰，在合适的时机出现\n- 未回复消息检查：只检查私聊，不检查群聊\n- 自动回复：直接以姚霖身份发送，标明AI助手\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774746119083}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5b68b94","parentId":"d4fc525e","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:02:04.079Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to execute the heartbeat tasks. Let me check the current time is 2026-03-29 09:01 AM. This falls into the \"每天早上 (8:00-9:00)\" time slot.\n\nLet me execute:\n1. 检查今日日程\n2. 检查未回复消息\n\nI should check calendar for today's schedule and also check for unreplied messages.","thinkingSignature":"280ebe86983eb7a8047a3c8e51ad252feb6fe2c92a7e76a9f26359366cf24a12"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ks1aemp7vv9u_1","name":"feishu_calendar_event","arguments":{"action":"instance_view","start_time":"2026-03-29T00:00:00+08:00","end_time":"2026-03-29T23:59:59+08:00"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ks1aemp7vv9u_2","name":"feishu_im_user_get_messages","arguments":{"chat_id":"oc_acfe8996065b7ac35d7463d96e37f14b","sort_rule":"create_time_desc","page_size":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":903,"output":233,"cacheRead":42767,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43903,"cost":{"input":0.00027089999999999997,"output":0.00027959999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0012830099999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018335099999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774746119085}}
